title: Should you have the ability to see how many views your items on the Bazaar have?
body: I think it would be helpful to know how many views your items on the bazaar have over a rolling 7 day and 30 day period. This will help people have the ability to better understand whether or not the item is listed in a way that is drawing interest.
author: 0x8e29B3F71a8c7276d122C88d9bf317e857ABb376
